The third most likely sub-category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), as the paper deals with information flow in closed loop systems. The fourth most likely sub-category is cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), as the paper deals with feedback loops and non-linear mappings. The fifth most likely sub-category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), as the paper deals with closed loop systems and information flow.
